channel.description:
Welcome to InsidiaX
This is InsidiaX, a free, RuneScape Private Server created by Insidia Team. we added lot of customs and better things like New Bosses,Minigames,Dungeoneering,Farming. and lot of additions, we hope you like it have a nice game! see you!
Other Informations
InsidiaX is a brand new server, we are dedicated to bringing the best enjoyment to all of our players. We are VPS hosted so that means 24/7 uptime, once you're here there is no need to leave. If you have a problem on Insidia, don't worry. A member of staff will be there to help you 100% along the way, regardless of your issue. We also have tons and tons of features that include various different bosses, minigames, shops and much much more. The only way you will know how good Insidia is, is by becoming part of this amazing experience. Jump in now and experience more than just a private server.
